"```sql\nSELECT l.status\nFROM cards c\nJOIN legalities l ON c.uuid = l.uuid\nWHERE c.frameVersion = '1997'\n  AND c.artist = 'D. Alexander Gregory'\n  AND c.hasContentWarning = 1\n  AND l.format = 'legacy';\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the status of cards that meet the specified conditions: they have a frame style version of 1997, are illustrated by D. Alexander Gregory, have sensitive content, and are in the legacy play format. The query uses a join between the `cards` and `legalities` tables based on the `uuid` foreign key relationship."